</P>
<P>
	SCOTTSDALE, Ariz. (AP) -- Bobby Francis, a Boston Bruins  
assistant, will be the next coach of the Phoenix Coyotes, according 
to media reports. The Coyotes declined today to comment on the 
reports, but confirmed that Phoenix assistant John Tortorella, 
considered the front-runner, would not be offered the job. 

</P>
