<HEADLINE> Magic Release Dominique Wilkins </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	ORLANDO, Fla. (AP) -- Nine-time NBA All-Star Dominique Wilkins  
was waived Monday after appearing in just 27 games and averaging 
five points for the Orlando Magic this season. 
</P>
<P>
	Wilkins, 39, averaged 24.8 points, 6.7 rebounds and 2.5 assists  
during his 15-year career and is eighth on the league's all-time 
scoring list with 26,668 points. 
</P>
<P>
	He signed with Orlando as a free agent on Feb. 5, but averaged  
less than 10 minutes of playing time. 
  	   	
