</P>
<P>
	The Justice Department has demanded the Hartford, Conn.-based  
insurer divest itself of some operations in Texas as a condition 
its company's pending $1 billion acquisition of the health care 
unit of Prudential Insurance Co. of America. 

</P>
<P>
	Becton Dickinson, down 8 3/4 at 30 3/8  
</P>
<P>
