<HEADLINE>  McEnroe Tops Courier in Exhibition </HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
	NEWPORT, R.I. (AP) -- Don't let the gray hair on John McEnroe's  
head fool you, warned Jim Courier. The 40-year-old McEnroe proved 
he can still play a pretty good game of tennis. 
</P>
<P>
